              "note": "**Spahn-led CDU/CSU delegation tells Beijing the Ukraine war is the binding constraint on the relationship**: At the CCG-KAS dialogue ahead of the 14th CPC-CDU/CSU Party Dialogue, Jens Spahn called China's backing of Russia \"the greatest challenge in its relationship with Europe and Germany\" and pressed Beijing to use its leverage on Putin; he also flagged that Germany has been losing \"10,000 industrial jobs every month for the last two or three years\" to overcapacity and subsidies, signalling the incoming government will not soften its line ([CCG transcript](https://www.ccgupdate.org/p/transcript-german-cducsu-delegation)).",
